        <div class="note">
            <p class="Note-Text">If you wish to create a new file filter in an open project, select <span class="Emphasis">Tools &gt; File Filters</span>. In the File Filters dialog, select the <span class="Emphasis">File type</span> from the drop-down list. Then, follow the remaining steps for that file type to create the filter.</p>
